{"tid":2447920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲男生脫暴動罪 律政司申請上訴","createTime":"2021-03-15T14:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T14:18:17.000Z","uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f509310125f8f7bc1e566d6f23d6b0acb23d140","tid":2447920,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"過份咯，脫罪仲要被上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//前年8月31日港島區爆發多場示威衝突，警方在銅鑼灣一帶作驅散時，有示威者向警方投擲汽油彈，期間一名學生被截停及拘捕。該名學生事後被控一項暴動罪，於區域法院受審。主審法官姚勳智在上周二（9日）裁定該學生罪名不成立。律政司今天（15日）證實，律政司已根據《區域法院條例》第84條的規定，以案件呈述的方式提出上訴。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWLkBKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWLkBKK.jpg&h=b817b184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/19%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%84%AB%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-113027119.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F19%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2584%25AB%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-113027119.html&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=174abb6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/19%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%84%AB%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-113027119.html</a>"},{"pid":"83f8fa9208836c08480e933a90d828c7dbebadf2","tid":2447920,"uid":13250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"Youtuber誠誠？"},{"pid":"786a35234f8a133a3b10dfffacf7211d78d8c392","tid":2447920,"uid":267801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:18:17.000Z","msg":"其實每次上訴都是使納稅人幾多錢！"}]}